notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-12T14:01:40.602Z",codex,"Verified release readiness after moving @unbrained/pm-cli to runtime dependencies: npm release:check completed for the fleet on 2026-06-12; npm audit retries for pm-beads and pm-jira returned 0 vulnerabilities after transient advisory endpoint failures."
body: "Align to latest published @unbrained/pm-cli, align pm-changelog where applicable, verify changelog/release commands, run tests with real package data, and record upstream pm CLI/SDK UX issues separately in unbraind/pm-cli.\n\n2026-06-12 PR #15 review/CI fix: GitHub CI failure was Verify generated changelog; local changelog:check is now up to date. Addressed Sourcery/Gemini portability feedback by using node:path basename for snapshot labels and tests, and computing one snapshotDate for JSON payload date plus --history-dir filename so midnight boundary cannot split them. Verification: npm run build, npm run build:test, npm test (67 passing), npm run check, npm run changelog:check."
